24:23.200 --> 24:24.842
I learned it in Germany, in German.

24:25.964 --> 24:29.107
And now I've got seven verses and that one right there.

24:30.969 --> 24:37.056
A timing of God is simply sovereignly wise and seldom your timing.

24:37.997 --> 24:39.099
God knows what he's doing.

24:39.159 --> 24:39.599
We wait.

24:39.960 --> 24:42.002
Waiting is a huge part.

24:42.338 --> 24:43.920
of the Christian life.

24:45.883 --> 24:47.586
Evil doers will be cut off.

24:47.666 --> 24:55.538
This is Psalm 37, but those who wait for the Lord, they will inherit the land.

24:56.579 --> 25:09.138
A great part of waiting is meekness and humility, because a verse, two verses later it says, the humble will inherit the land.

