So you're sitting in a doctor's office and he had an emergency and he's not there.

25:34.078 --> 25:39.666
And the appointments are backing up and this room is full

25:40.994 --> 25:42.115
upset people.

25:44.177 --> 25:49.983
Now, who are the people who are making themselves a perfect pain in their rear for these poor receptionists?

25:51.665 --> 25:54.368
Proud people, not humble people.

25:55.028 --> 26:01.134
People who presume upon their rights, the humble people understand reality.

26:02.336 --> 26:04.478
Nobody's planned anything against you here.

26:05.219 --> 26:06.800
